.. -*- restructuredtext -*-

==============
Cannula
==============

This is the basis of the client and server tools written in django to deploy
applications to a production environment. It is highly customizable and easy to
write new plugins for anything you can think of. 

Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Pycrypto >= 2.0.1
* Paramiko 
* Django >= 1.2.3
* virtualenv >= 1.5.1

Documentation 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Developer documentation are located in the 'docs/build/html/' directory. The 
documentation can be built with the command 'make html'. You will need to
have sphinx installed to build the docs.

End-user documentation is located on the http://bitbucket.org/rmyers/cannula
